Africa's Next Top Model - Season 1, Episode 6




Township Couture

After an intense series of events, the girls were understandably wary of the next Oluchi Mail. But to their surprise, it was an invitation to explore the beauty of Cape Town. For their next challenge, the models have to wear Marianne Fassler's Summer Couture collection with a special guest for the photo shoot.




Original Air Date: 15-Dec-2013
